				<td colspan="2"><span>I am totally on board with you Steppy on the 24 person raid.  Right now, on 50+ person raids, I hardly feel as if I matter.  h*ll, I can go /afk on 98% of battles and not effect the outcome a single bit.
<br />

<br />
One of my biggest pet peeves about EQ1 is the entire 50 PC vs 1 NPC idea.  Bleh.  I'd much rather see 12 players taking on 12 NPC or 24 NPC.  In a battle like that, hopefully everyone has an active part in &quot;controlling&quot; the flow of battle and not simply piling on<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
